description: Two women and a visa consultant from Mehsana attempted to deceive the US embassy and immigration authorities by forging documents for non-immigrant visas, leading to a complaint filed by Eric Molitor for visa fraud.
title: US embassy files FIR against 2 Gujarat girls

description: Accused Vijay Palande challenges the reinstatement of Ujjwal Nikam as special public prosecutor in his murder cases, alleging malafide intentions and political bias. Nikam, BJP's nominee in Mumbai North Central, resigned from cases before election campaigning. Palande seeks cancellation of Nikam's appointment, fearing false convictions and unfair treatment.
title: Murder accused challenges Ujjwal Nikam’s return

description: Delhi's tax revenue in 2023-24 surged to Rs 53,680 crore, exceeding govt estimates. GST rose by 15.6%, stamp duty revenue by over 28%. Atishi projected a 9.5% revenue increase for 2024-25, with an expected economic growth of 9.2% and per capita income growth of 7.4%.
title: 13% rise in Delhi's tax revenue in 2023-24

description: A senior Airports Authority official was found dead under suspicious circumstances at his official accommodation at the airport. TOI is withholding his name. The official was found hanging from a ceiling fan dressed in women's clothes, including a maxi, undergarments, bindi, lipstick, and bangles. His wife, a teacher, was in Pithoragarh at the time of the incident.
title: Senior airport official found hanging dressed as a woman

description: Indian IT service providers like TCS, HCLTech, Wipro, and Tech Mahindra have restructured their businesses and leadership teams in response to a slowdown in demand. They are focusing on building new capabilities in generative artificial intelligence (Gen AI) and AI-driven human-machine collaboration platforms.
title: Indian IT companies undergoing a shift: Here’s what’s changing

description: Elon Musk, CEO of Tesla, welcomed his twelfth child with Shivon Zilis, director at Neuralink, emphasizing his concerns about declining birth rates.
title: Elon Musk welcomes his 12th child; says it’s no 'secret'
